article_title: Ice Fishing Tournament Back At Catfish Bay
article_text:
Sioux Falls, SD

The 4th Annual Pre-Drilled Hole Ice Fishing Tournament is back at Catfish Bay.

The gates open at 10:30 a.m. with the tournament going from 1 to 4 p.m. The open competition has a $1,000 first place prize and a $200 first place prize for those 12-years-old and under. There are various prizes available as well.

Tickets for the tournament can be purchased at the gate. Adults are $40 per ticket and $25 for kids 12 and under.
